   @{B}AppMenu@{UB} and @{B}AppMenuCx@{UB} are written in C and compiled with SAS/C 6.55.
They are tested on an Amiga 3000 (2.0 and 3.1) with "Enforcer" and "Mungwall".

   If you want to create catalogs file of your language use the included
